@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam roundCorner 15
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
[*] --> Cancelled
Cancelled --> Pending : submit
Cancelled : entry / log author
Pending --> Closed : update
Closed --> Created : cancel
Created --> Rejected : confirm
Created : entry / log author
Rejected --> Draft : reject
Rejected : entry / log author
Draft --> [*]
@enduml